{
  "texts": [
    "Patients controlled the rehabilitation game with the Leap Motion controller on their hand, and the difficulty of the game was determined adaptively according to the movements of patients.",
    "The movement data was transferred to the cloud, where clinicians could view it.",
    "Patients were able to use the VRehab platform resulting in improvements in Upper Extremity Fugl-Meyer and hand kinematics.",
    "Sobrino et al.",
    "56 To evaluate the perceived usefulness and ease of use of VRehab platform."
  ]
}